<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="2Jul1919"><font color="red">2 July 1919</font>, <cite>Letters I</cite> (JJ to Harriet Weaver): As regards my book <cite>Ulysses</cite> it will not be finished, I suppose, for a year or so &hellip; I forwarded some time ago the chapter <cite>Wandering Rocks</cite> to Mr Pound but it was not acknowledged. Was a copy of the typescript forwarded to you? I also sent him in France the episode of the <cite>Sirens</cite>. This, at least, reached him and he told me he had sent it on to you and to Miss Anderson. I fear he does not like the book. I shall send the episode of the <cite>Cyclops</cite> next &mdash; but when I cannot say</div>
